lead_paragraph: Luuk de Jong’s early goal set PSV Eindhoven on their way to a 3-1 victory at Excelsior in the Dutch league on Wednesday that moved them to within one point of leaders Ajax Amsterdam.

headline.print_headline: PSV Win at Excelsior to Close on Dutch Leaders Ajax
